fields.description: Developed and maintained web applications using Django, Python, and MySQL with focus on Indigenous language preservation.
fields.responsibilities:
Developed and maintained web applications using Django, Python, and MySQL with database integration and user authentication systems
Converted legacy codebase to modern framework architecture, improving system performance, maintainability, and code optimization
Built educational platforms supporting Indigenous language preservation with multimedia content delivery and interactive features
Utilized DBMS tools and version control (Git) for efficient project management while debugging and optimizing web application modules
Collaborated with faculty on research-driven, data-centric solutions for Indigenous knowledge system projects and IT integration
fields.technologies_used: Django, Python, MySQL, Git, HTML5, CSS, JavaScript

fields.description: Performing real-time calculations and providing exceptional customer service in a fast-paced casino environment.
fields.responsibilities:
Performing real-time mental arithmetic to calculate bets, payouts, and odds quickly and accurately
Providing exceptional customer service, engaging with players, explaining game rules, and maintaining a welcoming and professional environment
Developing faster and more efficient mental techniques to calculate payouts, improving game flow, and reducing dealer processing time
Ensure compliance with all legal, regulatory, and industry standards to maintain operational integrity
